To solve the problem, we need to complete the proof of FKS Theorem 3.1. The theorem statement is:

```tactics
theorem theorem_3_1 {x T : ℝ} (hx : x > exp 50) (hodd : ∃ X, Odd X ∧ x = X / 2) (hT : T ∈ Set.Ioo 50 x) : Eψ x ≤ (riemannZeta.zeroes_sum (Set.Ioo 0 1) (Set.Ioo (-T) T) fun ρ => ‖↑x ^ (ρ - 1) / ρ‖) + 2 * log x ^ 2 / T := by
